# Meta API Credentials for Instagram Caption Generator

# Get these from: https://developers.facebook.com/apps/
# 1. Create app → Business → Instagram API
# 2. Get Instagram Business Account ID
# 3. Generate access token with permissions:
#    - instagram_basic
#    - pages_read_engagement

META_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_long_access_token_here
INSTAGRAM_BUSINESS_ID=your_instagram_business_account_id

# Optional: For extended access token generation
META_APP_ID=your_app_id
META_APP_SECRET=your_app_secret

# Usage:
# 1. Copy this file to .env
# 2. Fill in your actual credentials
# 3. Never commit .env to git (already in .gitignore)
